@startuml C4_Pattern_Exception
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Workflow Pattern - Exception Handling

Boundary(exception_flow, "Exception Handling Flow") {
    Component(task, "Task", "Execution", "Regular task")
    Component(exception_thrown, "Exception", "Event", "Task fails")
    Component(exception_router, "ExceptionRouter", "Logic", "Route exceptions")
    Component(exception_handler, "ExceptionHandler", "Task", "Handle error")
    Component(recovery_task, "RecoveryTask", "Task", "Compensate")
    Component(escalation, "Escalation", "Task", "Notify admin")
}

exception_flow: task --> exception_thrown: Throws
exception_thrown --> exception_router: Routes to
exception_router --> exception_handler: Specific handler
exception_handler --> recovery_task: Compensate
recovery_task --> exception_router: Success?
exception_router --> escalation: If unrecoverable

Note as N1
Exception Types:
- Task exception (task fails)
- Timeout exception (SLA violation)
- Resource exception (unavailable)
- Data exception (validation fail)

Handler Actions:
- Compensate (undo changes)
- Retry (with backoff)
- Escalate (to admin)
- Abort (fail fast)
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
